rows.label: qst202902_msg0001
rows.name:
What's this?
A visitor, at this time of night?

rows.label: qst202902_msg0003
rows.name:
It does seem a bit late...
Come on in, the door's open!

rows.label: qst202902_msg0002
rows.name:
Sorry to call on you at this late hour.
Is there a woman by the name of
Tsuki here?

rows.label: qst202902_msg0004
rows.name:
That'd be me, hon.
What's troubling you?

rows.label: qst202902_msg0005
rows.name:
It's my daughter, Kastina.
She hasn't come home this evening.

rows.label: qst202902_msg0006
rows.name:
She said she'd been talking to someone
called Tsuki recently, so I thought you
might have some idea where she went.

rows.label: qst202902_msg0007
rows.name:
Oh, that little girl who took
a shine to her...

rows.label: qst202902_msg0008
rows.name:
You answered a bunch of questions
for her, right, Tsuki?

rows.label: qst202902_msg0009
rows.name: Well, she just kept asking!

rows.label: qst202902_msg0010
rows.name: Now let me think...

rows.label: qst202902_msg0011
rows.name:
It's just an idea, but she might've gone
looking for Moondrops.

rows.label: qst202902_msg0012
rows.name: I told her they only bloom at night, see.

rows.label: qst202902_msg0013
rows.name:
Y-you mean she might be wandering
outside of Teos Aure right now?!

rows.label: qst202902_msg0014
rows.name: Well, I can't say for sure...

rows.label: qst202902_msg0022
rows.name: But I guess this is probably my fault.

rows.label: qst202902_msg0015
rows.name:
You wait right here, an' I'll go see
if I can't bring your daughter home
safe and sound.

rows.label: qst202902_msg0016
rows.name:
Thank you so much...
Please do find her!

rows.label: qst202902_msg0017
rows.name:
You might want to try asking her
friends if she said anything.

rows.label: qst202902_msg0023
rows.name:
I was going to ask them next,
if I didn't have any luck here...

rows.label: qst202902_msg0024
rows.name:
All right, I'll go see about asking them
first. Could you tell me their names?

rows.label: qst202902_msg0018
rows.name:
There's Celesmia, who's usually in the
Residential Area...and Manegal, who
I often see in Soprac Old Market.

rows.label: qst202902_msg0019
rows.name:
Oh, and Lieselotte. You can probably
find her in Elmos Square.

rows.label: qst202902_msg0020
rows.name:
Thanks a bunch. Don't you worry, I'll
find little Kastina before you know it.

rows.label: qst202902_msg0021
rows.name: You just sit tight an' stay strong.
